title: 'Poor quality product - Plastic material used of pathetic quality'
body: 'The media could not be loaded. This product is It has four wheels. In just one use it base body cracked near wheel. Now it not able to stand  it bends making the cart unsteady when it tries to stand. It is tumbling from the front.  When reached to customer care for warranty claim - I got a standard response it is mishandling of the product and this is not covered. So my advice to all not to buy this product. It useless and made of poor quality material and safari is give false warranty. It is of same quality as road side bag seller who selling it much cheaper.  Their customer service Safari <customercare@safari.in> want us to treat luggage as show piece to decorate drawing room and do not put in use. Because if you use it break and they are exposed what they are selling to customer'
